      <title>PM警告说，杂货连锁店在澳大利亚面临罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/grocery-chains-face-fines-in-australia-over-pricing-pm-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚的杂货店零售商将面临高昂的罚款，以使价格上涨或在拟议的政府改革下提供伪造折扣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/grocery-chains-face-fines-in-australia-over-pricing-pm-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 01:04:48 GMT</pubDate>
